author: Special Correspondent
title: ‘Samples lifted from 70 ‘high-risk contacts’
description: They were closely associated with 17 COVID positive patients
content:
Samples from 70 high-risk contacts, who were closely associated with 17 COVID-19 positive cases from the district have been lifted for analysis, while 158 low-risk contacts have been put in home quarantine, Collector Sandeep Nanduri said on Thursday.
